went into science.

1032
01:00:46.226 --> 01:00:48.145
I did.

1033
01:00:48.228 --> 01:00:51.732
R-Force is my creation.
I’m the lead researcher.

1034
01:00:51.815 --> 01:00:54.360
Wow. Come on.

1035
01:00:54.443 --> 01:00:56.612
Yeah, I have a PhD
in biotechnology

1036
01:00:56.695 --> 01:01:00.115
