I came down here to see
if she needed help.

1288
01:22:35.117 --> 01:22:36.494
I should’ve known.

1289
01:22:36.577 --> 01:22:38.204
Is that right?

1290
01:22:39.789 --> 01:22:42.333
You would know
more than anyone, right?

