1379
01:27:55.521 --> 01:27:57.439
I want my chopper on the pad
ready to fly.

1380
01:27:57.523 --> 01:27:59.441
-We’re on our way.
-PILOT: I copy, Colonel.

1381
01:27:59.525 --> 01:28:01.735
This is Viper One
